==Description==

La commande [[Image:Fasteners_RestoreProperties.svg|24px]] '''Fasteners Restaurer''' permet de restaurer les objets de fixation enregistrés sans l'atelier Fasteners.

[[Image:Fasteners_RestoreProperties_Example.png]]
{{Caption|L'[[Tree_View/fr|arborescence]] indiquant les éléments de fixation à restaurer}}

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Utilisation==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Select the {{MenuCommand|Fasteners → [[Image:Fasteners_RestoreProperties.svg|16px]] Restore fasteners}} option from the menu.
# All fasteners in the document are checked and restored if required.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Notes==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The fasteners should still have all their properties. Fasteners that have been simplified with [[Image:Fasteners_Simplify.svg|16px]] [[Fasteners_Simplify|Simplify shape]] cannot be restored.
</div>


